Class TUCaptureRequestVO

java.lang.Object
org.openwms.wms.receiving.api.CaptureRequestVO
org.openwms.wms.receiving.api.TUCaptureRequestVO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TUCaptureRequestVO extends CaptureRequestVO implements Serializable
A TUCaptureRequestVO contains all information used to capture goods within a LoadUnit on top of an expected TransportUnit.
Author:
Heiko Scherrer
